snippet.title: BiteVille | Teaser trailer
snippet.description:
BiteVille will release to steam on the 23rd of October (just in time for Spooky-halloween). Wishlisting our game would help us out a lot :)
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1345380/BiteVille/

The world has fallen victim to a deadly virus, zombies now roam the lands. While running for your life you stumble upon a small city. Claim this city as your own, protect it with your life and maybe other survivors will find you. 

Stay updated by joining our reddit and discord!
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/BiteVille/
Discord:https://discord.com/invite/VFySG8H
